# ⚠️  PRODUCTION CONFIGURATION - SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH
# This file is committed to the repository to prevent configuration regression
# Any changes must be reviewed and tested before deployment
#
# Configuration change process:
# 1. Understand what the variable controls
# 2. Test changes in development environment first
# 3. Create PR with clear description of changes
# 4. Get review from team lead
# 5. Deploy to staging and verify
# 6. Deploy to production

